snippet.title: Meghan markle did not lie over archie's skin color comment, new book claims. Not suprising at all.
snippet.description:
#MeghanMarkle #Princecharles #Archie

remember when meghan markle said there were multiple instances when concerns about archie skin color was voiced in the palace. people said she was lying as Prince harry only spoke about one instance. well a new book on royal wives, kate and  meghan confirms just that. Christopher Andersen's book comfirms that conversation between prince charles and camila did take place around the time harry and meghan were engaged to be married and also after she fell pregnant.
tags: Meghan markle and prince harry news
